<placeName>Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" type="edition"><div n="r,1" type="textpart"><!--milestone unit="4"--><ab>

    <lb n="1"/>κυρίῳ μου ἀδελφῷ Ἀπολλωνίωι 

    <lb n="2"/><expan><hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>πομνηματογρ<ex>άφῳ</ex></expan> <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>οῦστος <expan>χαίρει<ex>ν</ex></expan>. 

    <lb n="3"/>ἔγραψέν μοι ὁ υ<hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>ὸς Διοσκουρίδης 

    <lb n="4"/>περὶ Διογένους τοῦ υ<hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>οῦ Μαρκέλ

    <lb n="5" type="worddiv"/>λης ὡς τεθνεῶτος καὶ ἐχρῆν 

    <lb n="6"/>σε, κύριέ μου ἄδελφε, εἰδότα ὡς 

    <lb n="7"/>σοῦ χάριν ἐνθάδε <choice><corr>διατρίβω</corr><sic>διατριβων</sic></choice>, 

    <lb n="8"/>κήδεσθαι καὶ <choice><corr>φροντίζειν</corr><sic>φροντιδειν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="9"/>τοῦ πράγματος <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>πὲρ τοῦ <choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημειν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="10"/>λυσιτελοῦντος. οἶδας γάρ, <choice><corr>καὶ ἐὰν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="11"/>ἐγὼ μὴ γράφω σοι, ὡς τὰ τῶν 

    <lb n="12"/>ἀπελευθέρων <choice><corr>ὑποστέλλει</corr><sic><hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>ποστέλλειν</sic></choice> τοῖς 

    <lb n="13"/>πάτρωσι. καλῶς οὖν ποιήσεις, 

    <lb n="14"/>ἀναλαβών μου τὸ πρόσωπον, 

    <lb n="15"/>ποιήσας τὸν υ<hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>όν μου Διοσκου

    <lb n="16" type="worddiv"/><unclear>ρί</unclear>δην ἐπ᾽ ἀναγραφῇ ἔχειν 

    <lb n="17"/><supplied reason="lost">τά τε</supplied> <unclear>κ</unclear>τήνη καὶ τὴν συνκο

    <lb n="18" type="worddiv"/><supplied reason="lost">μιδὴ</supplied><unclear>ν</unclear> καὶ εἴ τι ἄλλο αὐτῷ 

    <lb n="19"/><gap extent="4" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>νεν, πρ<unclear>ώτ</unclear>ως ποιη

    <lb n="20" type="worddiv"/><gap extent="5" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear>ο</unclear>μιλω<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ος αὐτὸν 

    <lb n="21"/><gap extent="4" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ι τῶν ἐκεῖ ἀποκει

    <lb n="22" type="worddiv"/><supplied reason="lost">μένων</supplied> βιβλίων ἕνεκεν 

    <lb n="23"/><gap extent="4" reason="lost" unit="character"/> <unclear>π</unclear>άντα τὰ ἔνγραφα 

    <lb n="24"/><gap extent="4" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> ἀπόκ<unclear>ε</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied>ται. οἶδεν 

    <lb n="25"/><supplied reason="lost">Διοσκ</supplied><unclear>ο</unclear>υρίδη<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied> <unclear>ο</unclear>ὗ λέγω 

    <lb n="26"/><gap extent="5" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear>ρ</unclear>εν<unclear>τ</unclear><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="2" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ων καὶ 

    <lb n="27"/><gap extent="5" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> κατὰ <unclear>τ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">οὺς</supplied> νόμους 

    <lb n="28"/><gap extent="5" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ωσκα<gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><expan><gap extent="1" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied>λθὼ<ex>ν</ex></expan> 

